title: Looking for determined duo partner to climb out of bronze
body:
I'm looking for some duo partners to climb up to at least silver. I can play all positions fairly well but my preference is mid>top>sup>jg>adc. 
I own all champs and can play most of them fairly well. I'm able to play almost everyday at night. 
So add me if you are keen. Looking forward to see you on the rift. ^-^

replies.body:
I'm silver currently and I can duo if you'd like, my main is support almost exclusively but i can play other lanes to a satisfactory extent.

I too only play at night so i think our schedules to be alright.
